WEBVTT

00:01.034 --> 00:02.729
<i>Previously on "Heartland"...</i>

00:02.836 --> 00:05.031
No, Lisa, you are interfering
in my life.

00:05.138 --> 00:07.231
Giving out my e-mail address
to some guy I don't even know

00:07.340 --> 00:09.399
because my love life
is just so pathetic.

00:09.509 --> 00:11.534
Who do you think you are?

00:11.644 --> 00:16.581
I don't know that I have ever been
so disappointed in you.

00:16.683 --> 00:19.117
It's Ashley. I swear she calls me
like 10 times a day.

00:19.219 --> 00:19.810
Really?

00:19.919 --> 00:21.511
Yeah, her mom's
still driving her nuts.

00:21.621 --> 00:22.713
Oh, poor baby.

00:22.822 --> 00:25.757
Hey, I like her.
She's a good kid.

00:32.698 --> 00:33.791
"Hi, there, stranger.

00:33.900 --> 00:37.301
For whatever reason,
I'm thinking about you.

00:37.404 --> 00:39.133
I want fate to make its move.

00:39.239 --> 00:40.297
Peter."

00:41.608 --> 00:42.802
<i>Carpe diem.</i>

